{
  "n8n_workflow_template": {
    "name": "Claude AI Integration",
    "nodes": [
      {
        "name": "Webhook",
        "type": "n8n-nodes-base.webhook",
        "parameters": {
          "httpMethod": "POST",
          "path": "claude-chat",
          "responseMode": "responseNode",
          "options": {}
        },
        "position": [250, 300]
      },
      {
        "name": "Claude API",
        "type": "n8n-nodes-base.httpRequest",
        "parameters": {
          "method": "POST",
          "url": "https://api.anthropic.com/v1/messages",
          "authentication": "genericCredentialType",
          "genericAuthType": "headerAuth",
          "sendHeaders": true,
          "headerParameters": {
            "parameters": [
              {
                "name": "x-api-key",
                "value": "YOUR_ANTHROPIC_API_KEY_HERE"
              },
              {
                "name": "anthropic-version",
                "value": "2023-06-01"
              }
            ]
          },
          "sendBody": true,
          "bodyParameters": {
            "parameters": [
              {
                "name": "model",
                "value": "claude-3-haiku-20240307"
              },
              {
                "name": "max_tokens",
                "value": 1024
              },
              {
                "name": "messages",
                "value": "[{\"role\": \"user\", \"content\": \"{{ $json.body }}\"}]"
              }
            ]
          },
          "options": {}
        },
        "position": [500, 300],
        "credentials": {
          "headerAuth": {
            "name": "Anthropic API",
            "id": "1"
          }
        }
      },
      {
        "name": "Respond to Webhook",
        "type": "n8n-nodes-base.respondToWebhook",
        "parameters": {},
        "position": [750, 300]
      }
    ],
    "connections": {
      "Webhook": {
        "main": [
          [
            {
              "node": "Claude API",
              "type": "main",
              "index": 0
            }
          ]
        ]
      },
      "Claude API": {
        "main": [
          [
            {
              "node": "Respond to Webhook",
              "type": "main",
              "index": 0
            }
          ]
        ]
      }
    }
  },
  "instructions": "1. Abre n8n (http://localhost:5678)\n2. Ve a Settings > Credentials\n3. Crea una nueva credencial 'Header Auth'\n   - Name: Anthropic API\n   - Header Name: x-api-key\n   - Header Value: TU_API_KEY_DE_ANTHROPIC_AQUI\n4. Crea un nuevo workflow\n5. Añade los nodos: Webhook > HTTP Request > Respond to Webhook\n6. Configura el HTTP Request como se indica arriba (usando la credencial segura, no la clave en texto plano)\n7. Activa el workflow"
}

